      • goToSlide

        public boolean goToSlide(int position)
        Tries to go to the given position and will stop when canGoForward() or canGoBackward() returns false.
        参数:
        position - The position the pager should go to.
        返回:
        true if the pager was able to go the complete way to the given position, false otherwise.

      • nextSlide

        public boolean nextSlide()
        Tries to go to the next slide if canGoForward() returns true.
        返回:
        true if the pager was able to go to the next slide, false otherwise.

      • previousSlide

        public boolean previousSlide()
        Tries to go to the previous slide if canGoForward() returns true.
        返回:
        true if the pager was able to go to the previous slide, false otherwise.

      • goToLastSlide

        public boolean goToLastSlide()
